**Iteration 3 complete.** Files written: `iterations/iteration-003.md`, `state-parts/iter-003.jsonl`, `deltas/iter-003.jsonl` (9 findings). Used 9 tool calls (4 grounding reads/globs + 2 prior-iteration reads + 1 spec read + 2 new advisor-scorer reads), under the 12-call budget. The headline result: RQ3 resolves to **two separate sub-scores** (inter-skill advisor + intra-skill in-SKILL.md router) feeding a **five-stage "properly utilized" funnel**, and RQ4 resolves to a **three-tier fixture taxonomy** whose T1‚ÜîT2 gap is the circularity meter ‚Äî directly modeled on the advisor's already-shipped corpus/holdout split (80.5% / 77.5%).
